  "translations": {
    "en": "And of the ascension of the Prophet to the seventh heaven, and from it to the Lote Tree of the Furthest Boundary, and from it to the veils of light, and of the private conversation of God with him. And that he was ascended with his body and his spirit in soundness and reality, not as a vision in sleep. And that was not because God is in a place there, for He is exalted above location, but rather He ascended him as an honour and an exaltation of his rank, and to show him the kingdom of the heavens just as He had shown him the kingdom of the Earth, and to witness what is in them of the might of God, and so that he may inform his nation of what he witnessed in the heights of signs and evidences.",
    "ur": "اور نبی کے معراج کا ساتویں آسمان تک، اور وہاں سے سدرة المنتہیٰ تک، اور وہاں سے نور کے پردوں تک، اور اللہ عزوجل کی مناجات۔ اور یہ کہ آپ کو جسم اور روح دونوں کے ساتھ صحت اور حقیقت میں معراج کرایا گیا۔",
    "tr": "Ve Peygamber'in yedinci semaya miracının, oradan Sidretü'l-Münteha'ya, oradan nur perdelerine, ve Allah'in onunla münacatının ikrarı.",
    "fa": "و معراج پیامبر به آسمان هفتم، و از آنجا به سدرة المنتهی، و از آنجا به حجاب‌های نور، و مناجات خداوند با او.",
